  "text": "We use the X 2 -metric to compare individual descriptors. This was found to give a significant improvement over least squares in a recent study [CITATION_1] , while still being much faster than the more sophisticated Earth-movers distance. The final matching score is given as the ratio between the best and the second best dissimilarities,",
